        "subject": "b=14929  Handle ost numbering and info parsing in test suite",
        "message": "b=14929  Handle ost numbering and info parsing in test suite\n\nBy default the osts start their numbering at one but some of test use plain 'ost ' which in the\ntest suite causes it to default to zero which is incorrect. There are some off by one errors fixed\nas well. Discovered when using a large number of OSTs that ostuuid_from_index returns more than one\nvalue. Also some uuid mapping functions where created.\n\nChange-Id: I7e532b9f877b21613a562bf5ecf4ca5ad7f6322c\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
